      <h1 id="title">Mokhtar Dahari</h1>
      <p>the best soccer player in Malaysia at the time</p>
      <div id="img-div">
        <img id="image" src="amd.webp" />
        <p id="img-caption">
          Mokhtar Dahari was a Malaysian footballer from Setapak, Kuala Lumpur.
          He was given the nickname because of his prowess on the field strenght
          and scoring ability throughout his career.
        </p>
      </div>
      <br />
      <div id="tribute-info">
        <label for="career-info">
          Senior Career info
          <ul>
            <li><span>1972-1987</span> - Played for Selangor FC</li>
            <li><span>1978</span> - Played for Sultan Sulaiman Club</li>
            <li><span>1971-1987</span> - Played for Manchester United</li>
            <li><span>1984-1987</span> - Played for Kedah FA</li>
            <li><span>1988</span> - Played for Paris Saint German</li>
          </ul>
          National Team
          <ul>
            <li><span>1972-1985</span> - Malaysia</li>
          </ul>
        </label>
      </div>

